{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://Vinnl.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"Point Clear Martello Tower (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the 19th-century <b><a href=\"/wiki/Point_Clear_Martello_Tower\" title=\"Point Clear Martello Tower\">Point Clear Martello Tower</a></b> <i>(pictured)</i> now houses an aviation museum?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Point_Clear_Martello_Tower","retrieved":1781339808971},{"title":"Jimmy Whalen (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that, when baseball <a href=\"/wiki/Pitcher\" title=\"Pitcher\">pitcher</a> <b><a href=\"/wiki/Jimmy_Whalen_(baseball)\" title=\"Jimmy Whalen (baseball)\">Jimmy Whalen</a></b> was promoted to the <a href=\"/wiki/Major_League_Baseball\" title=\"Major League Baseball\">Major Leagues</a>, he refused to report because the team would not pay his travel expenses?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jimmy_Whalen_(baseball)","retrieved":1781339808972},{"title":"Australian Antarctic Territory (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that Australia took Japan to the International Court of Justice for its whaling activities near the <b><a href=\"/wiki/Australian_Antarctic_Territory\" title=\"Australian Antarctic Territory\">Australian Antarctic Territory</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Australian_Antarctic_Territory","retrieved":1781339808973},{"title":"Christopher Morcom (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <a href=\"/wiki/Alan_Turing\" title=\"Alan Turing\">Alan Turing</a> had a childhood crush on <b><a href=\"/wiki/Christopher_Morcom\" title=\"Christopher Morcom\">Christopher Morcom</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christopher_Morcom","retrieved":1781339808974},{"title":"Gropius House (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that a design competition for a bathroom outside the <b><a href=\"/wiki/Gropius_House\" title=\"Gropius House\">Gropius House</a></b> attracted 280 entries?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gropius_House","retrieved":1781339808978},{"title":"Nyamazana (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that warrior-queen <b><a href=\"/wiki/Nyamazana\" title=\"Nyamazana\">Nyamazana</a></b> defeated the last <a href=\"/wiki/Rozvi_Empire\" title=\"Rozvi Empire\">Rozvi</a> ruler, an act that has been miscredited to a male relative or <a href=\"/wiki/Mzilikazi\" title=\"Mzilikazi\">her husband</a>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nyamazana","retrieved":1781339808978},{"title":"a recent merger of American television station operators (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that one opponent of <b><a href=\"/wiki/Merger_of_Nexstar_Media_Group_and_Tegna_Inc.\" title=\"Merger of Nexstar Media Group and Tegna Inc.\">a recent merger of American television station operators</a></b> called it \"the most massive TV consolidation in history using a <a href=\"/wiki/Kangaroo_court\" title=\"Kangaroo court\">kangaroo process</a>\"?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Merger_of_Nexstar_Media_Group_and_Tegna_Inc.","retrieved":1781339808979},{"title":"Jōsaku Maeda (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that Japanese painter <b><a href=\"/wiki/J%C5%8Dsaku_Maeda\" title=\"Jōsaku Maeda\">Jōsaku Maeda</a></b> began consciously painting mandalas after critic <a href=\"/wiki/Konstanty_Jele%C5%84ski\" title=\"Konstanty Jeleński\">Konstanty Jeleński</a> described his <i>Night Series</i> as such in Paris in 1959?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/J%C5%8Dsaku_Maeda","retrieved":1781339808980},{"title":"Bite Me (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the choreography of \"<b><a href=\"/wiki/Bite_Me_(Enhypen_song)\" title=\"Bite Me (Enhypen song)\">Bite Me</a></b>\" prompted fans to send competing <a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_billboard\" title=\"Mobile billboard\">protest trucks</a> to the record label over the use of female backup dancers?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bite_Me_(Enhypen_song)","retrieved":1781339808981},{"title":"Destination of th